Summary of outbreaks
Total outbreaks: 3
Total animals affected
Species / Susceptible Cases / Deaths / Destroyed / Slaughtered
Birds / - / 5 / 0 / - / 0

Epidemiology
Source of the outbreak(s) or origin of infection: unknown or inconclusive
Epidemiological comments: gene sequencing shows that it is low pathogenic avian influenza virus (LPAI)

Control measures
Measures applied: control of wildlife reservoirs; quarantine; movement control inside the country; screening; zoning; disinfection of infected premises/establishment(s); dipping/spraying; no vaccination; no treatment of affected animals.

Measures to be applied: stamping out

